{"tid":813532,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★低位約21,000點左右，或最快今年10月至12月完成跌浪。","createTime":"2018-09-10T13:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T15:37:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb6f7f04ed774206172d5fd5185e4163fc6b4858","tid":813532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"雖然坊間有不少分析股市是否已陷入熊市的方法，但較常見的「圖表派」分析是跌穿250天線、50天線跌穿250天線，以及高位累挫兩成。周一(9月10日)以收市計，恒指已「三大皆凶」！<br />\n<br />\n那麼，後市怎看？若撇除2007至2008年金融海嘯，單計這3大信號，十年以來分別在2010至2011年及2015至2016年出現過，兩次事後均是累瀉約三成半，歷時約8至11個月！<br />\n<br />\n因此，若跟往績，今次港股頂位為1月所創的33,484點，累挫三成半的<span style=\"color: red;\">低位約21,000點左右，或最快今年10月至12月完成跌浪</span>。當然，歷史不會一模一樣重演，僅作參考。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180910/bkn-20180910181157380-0910_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180910%2Fbkn-20180910181157380-0910_00842_001.html&d=nxdefjDRBkq1KAagcTCPlzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4e39a9bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180910/bkn-20180910181157380-0910_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ce304ca6ba7702e28a744509853d8353fb945768","tid":813532,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"why not this??<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/225708_c048a748d4a407c53fee90e9acaee39f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F225708_c048a748d4a407c53fee90e9acaee39f.jpg&h=9ec7f95c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b613cb5ae1431423f2b7724ecdd45f0ccf1d9e05","tid":813532,"uid":53206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150a6bc7945433e9cdf521ac59b6de1ffc01ee9b","tid